  Locus:
    Page: 267
    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Imitation
---
We should not ignore the fact that it is left to us either to use or misuse
our mind and imagination. One who seeks God and depends upon God, who
trains his imagination to correspond with Divine imagination. ...lives in a
condition of peace and harmony.
